 2025-04492025-03-20GAC
ActSpecial Economic Measures Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Special Economic Measures (Haiti) Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the SPECIAL ECONOMIC MEASURES (HAITI) REGULATIONS in order to add three (3) individuals who are now subject to a broad dealings ban, to the list of persons under the Regulations in which individuals in Canada, as well as Canadians outside of Canada, are prohibited from dealing in the property of listed persons, entering into transactions with, providing services to them, transferring property to them, or otherwise making goods available them.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 2025-0111 Publication Date: 2025-04-09
AttachmentsAttachment
